<TITLE>CCL INDUSTRIES PURCHASES STAKE IN MONOBLOC</TITLE>
<DATELINE>    Toronto, April 8 - </DATELINE><BODY>&lt;CCL Industries Inc> said it purchased a
majority interest in Monobloc U.S.A. from Envases Metalurgicos
de Alava of Spain.
    Terms were not disclosed.
    CCL also said it agreed to exchange present and future
technology with Envases.
